    "description": "<p>Only possible as the first ability used this <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">TURN</span></strong></span>. You can engage or sustain a Run which lasts until the start of your next <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">TURN</span></strong></span> brings the following changes:</p><ul><li><p>Every time you use the Move Ability you can move an additional 3m which must be in a straight line.</p></li><li><p>Every consecetive move can only alter the direction by 45° unless 3 <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">MP</span></strong></span> are used for the Move used upon which the direction can be altered by 90°. Or alternativly 4 <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">MP</span></strong></span> can be used to stop early.</p></li><li><p>During a Run <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">AP</span></strong></span> can only be used for Dash, any other actions allow permissions by the GM, additionally someone running can't use Opportunity Attacks</p></li><li><p>While Running you recieve a +5 bonus to your <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">DODGE</span></strong></span> and a -5 penalty to your <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">STABILITY</span></strong></span></p></li></ul>",
